{"tid":2085808,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚耀宗：請放心！ 國安法「很多」做法按本港法律程序","createTime":"2020-06-30T04:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T06:52:53.000Z","uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"79cd50d5f6b5064bb1d98f42e1e21d4b52b7bef1","tid":2085808,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:57:50.000Z","msg":"全國人大常委譚耀宗表示，常委會早上全票通過港區國安法草案，基本法委員會稍後會開會討論，再由常委會決定是否將法例列入《基本法》附件三，在香港實施。被問到最高刑罰由10年修訂為終身監禁，是否「加辣」，<strong>譚耀宗表示，自己早前透露草案初審罰則後，社會有意見認為太輕。</strong>他不認為是「加辣」，而是<strong>按照國際上普遍對相關嚴重罪行的罰則</strong>，作出對稱的安排。<br />\n<br />\n對於香港眾志羅冠聰等人宣布退出香港眾志，法例是否有追溯力，追究有關人士以往的行為。譚耀宗表示，條文未正式公布，故不會深入討論，但條文對每個罪行有清楚界定，亦有談及追溯力的問題。至於陪審團安排，<strong>他表示，很多做法都會按照目前本港法律程序做，日後陪審團也有相應安排機制</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534869-20200630.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534869-20200630.htm&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CEy%2FESo4xB68IG1t9wT0pkU%3D&h=9de3f548\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534869-20200630.htm&h=7bc6a654\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534869-20200630.htm</a>"},{"pid":"309ba53a41b9e0c0565730536bf278efe2a52613","tid":2085808,"uid":155674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:59:10.000Z","msg":"okok"},{"pid":"65b49c61f6403a81220ad6344412a47b88c33ef2","tid":2085808,"uid":87,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T05:00:00.000Z","msg":"得架啦明架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82c9fe3042c1d6205f1c339240b41932639d5f7","tid":2085808,"uid":10441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"自己講自己笑"},{"pid":"913bd361fb447e2683a688f146c88272eef34cba","tid":2085808,"uid":226956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c